snippet.title: Quake - Shadow over Innsmouth
snippet.description:
Playthrough of "Shadow over Innsmouth" (shadow.bsp), a custom Q1 single player map made by Steve Rescoe. 

Note: This map is a sequel to "Village of Dread": 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4wEm1ao-bhs

Release Date: 06/03/1997
Download (shadow.zip):
https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/shadow.html

Skill 2 Hard
Secrets = 2/3
Kills = 128/128

Game: Quake
http://store.steampowered.com/app/2310/QUAKE/
Custom Engine: FTE 5121 (FTEQW by Spike)
http://fte.triptohell.info/index.php?p=downloads
Custom Models from Chillo's Model Pack v 1.6:
https://t.co/kHWCYN1E6Q 
and Authentic Model Improvement Collection:
http://www.quaketastic.com/files/models/auth_mdl163.zip
